text: Kampong Imang (Malay for Imang Village) is a village-level subdivision in Pengkalan Batu, a mukim in Brunei-Muara District, Brunei. It has the postcode BH3423. == Geography == As a subdivision, Kampong Imang borders Kampong Panchor Murai to the north, Kampong Wasan to the east and south, Kampong Birau to the south-west, Kampong Luagan Timbaran to the west, and Kampong Maraburong to the north-west. == References == Imang
